FTSE September Contract Daily Forecast - 05 September 2019

Jason SenStock Markets 3 hours ago (Sep 05, 2019 03:15AM ET) By

www.investing.com/analysis/ftse-september-contract-daily-forecast--05-september-2019-200461712 FTSE September Contract Daily Forecast - 05 September 2019 By By Jason Sen | 3 hours ago (Sep 05, 2019 03:15AM ET)

Follow Ftse September Contract Chart holding first support at 7325/20 is a buy signal targeting 7380/90. Above 7400 look for 7410, 7420, 7435 and 7455/60. Failure to hold above 7310 risks a slide to 7295/90 & 7270/66. A break below 7250 targets 7235 and 7220.
